00:15:27.560 --> 00:15:29.830
[screaming]

00:15:29.830 --> 00:15:30.990
what's going on?

00:15:30.990 --> 00:15:33.890
Yuma!

00:15:37.830 --> 00:15:39.360
Do Not fret about yuma.

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:41.690
He is just getting into
his role as my pawn!

00:15:41.690 --> 00:15:44.660
And now it is...
my draw!

00:15:44.660 --> 00:15:47.990
First, dark mist
will attack utopia!

00:15:47.990 --> 00:15:50.860
But not before mist
gains some power...

00:15:50.860 --> 00:15:54.960
from the shadows!

00:15:58.290 --> 00:16:00.890
I play utopia's
special ability!

00:16:00.890 --> 00:16:02.860
Light Wing shield!

00:16:02.860 --> 00:16:04.730
Nothing Can
protect him now!

00:16:04.730 --> 00:16:06.760
Not once I play...

00:16:06.760 --> 00:16:09.060
Overlay banish!

00:16:09.060 --> 00:16:11.830
It negates your monster's
special ability!

00:16:11.830 --> 00:16:13.860
But you know
what is not negated?

00:16:13.860 --> 00:16:17.060
Whiplash whirlwind!

00:16:25.830 --> 00:16:27.290
Get up, bronk!

00:16:27.290 --> 00:16:28.760
Yes Please do,

00:16:28.760 --> 00:16:32.460
so you can now see me destroy
your gearspring catapult!

00:16:32.460 --> 00:16:33.860
No way!

00:16:33.860 --> 00:16:35.590
Did you really think
that I was going to

00:16:35.590 --> 00:16:37.560
