00:16:37.560 --> 00:16:39.990
It is obvious you are
planning to use it to power up

00:16:39.990 --> 00:16:43.790
the next monster you summon.

00:16:43.790 --> 00:16:46.190
You're wrong.

00:16:46.190 --> 00:16:47.930
What bronk is planning
to do is take you

00:16:47.930 --> 00:16:50.590
down with a single
finishing blow.

00:16:50.590 --> 00:16:52.190
A single blow?

00:16:52.190 --> 00:16:55.730
Yes, his facedown card
is gearspring exploder.

00:16:55.730 --> 00:16:57.760
Don't give away
his strategy, yuma!

00:16:57.760 --> 00:16:59.130
No, do.

00:16:59.130 --> 00:17:01.660
I find this all
quite enlightening.

00:17:01.660 --> 00:17:03.490
You see, with
gearspring exploder,

00:17:03.490 --> 00:17:06.160
