turn and he gains counters,

00:17:06.160 --> 00:17:10.490
he'll deal 800 points of damage
for every counter that he has.

00:17:10.490 --> 00:17:12.090
800 points?

00:17:12.090 --> 00:17:13.630
So next turn...

00:17:13.630 --> 00:17:16.960
gearspring catapult and
automatic gearspring machine

00:17:16.960 --> 00:17:18.690
will each gain one counter for a

00:17:18.690 --> 00:17:20.160
total of four.

00:17:20.160 --> 00:17:23.890
And that will mean a total
of 3200 points of damage.

00:17:23.890 --> 00:17:27.230
If gearspring exploder
activates, we will be defeated.

00:17:27.230 --> 00:17:29.330
Thanks for the info.

00:17:29.330 --> 00:17:31.160
Yuma...

00:17:31.160 --> 00:17:32.560
in that case,

00:17:32.560 --> 00:17:34.960
I will just destroy
that facedown card.

00:17:34.960 --> 00:17:39.930
I am now activating the spell
xyz cyclone from my hand!

00:17:39.930 --> 00:17:43.060
With this card, if an xyz
monster was destroyed,

00:17:43.060 --> 00:17:46.460
one trap card is
destroyed, as well!

00:17:46.460 --> 00:17:49.430
so much for
gearspring exploder

00:17:49.430 --> 00:17:51.730
and with that,
I will end my turn...

00:17:51.730 --> 00:17:53.460
thank you, yuma.

00:17:53.460 --> 00:17:56.360
Always nice to get
the inside scoop.

00:17:56.360 --> 00:17:59.560
I can't believe it.
yuma sold me out.

00:18:03.530 --> 00:18:06.330
Your friend yuma has shown
me how to beat you.

00:18:06.330 --> 00:18:10.060
His loyalty to me
has sealed your doom!

00:18:10.060 --> 00:18:14.430
Give up now, and I
will show you mercy.

00:18:14.430 --> 00:18:17.530
"I won't give up, never ever!"

00:18:17.530 --> 00:18:19.530
same with me!

00:18:19.530 --> 00:18:20.590
I won't give up!

00:18:20.590 --> 00:18:23.830
just Like yuma never has!

00:18:23.830 --> 00:18:27.360
wait a sec, and maybe
he still hasn't.

00:18:27.360 --> 00:18:30.930
of course!

00:18:31.530 --> 00:18:32.730
Here goes,

00:18:32.730 --> 00:18:33.960
my draw!

00:18:33.960 --> 00:18:35.490
Perfect.

00:18:35.490 --> 00:18:37.630
First Things first!

00:18:37.630 --> 00:18:39.130
I put one counter on both

00:18:39.130 --> 00:18:43.960
gearspring catapult and
automatic gearspring machine!

00:18:43.960 --> 00:18:46.560
It is pointless to
keep fighting.

00:18:46.560 --> 00:18:48.030
Next I remove three counters

00:18:48.030 --> 00:18:51.290
from automatic gearspring
machine to summon...

00:18:51.290 --> 00:18:52.860
this!

00:18:52.860 --> 00:18:56.590
Gearspring spirit!

00:18:59.160 --> 00:19:00.990
With the power of
gearspring spirit,

00:19:00.990 --> 00:19:03.890
I can change one of your
monsters' attack points to 0

00:19:03.890 --> 00:19:05.830
until the end of this turn!

00:19:05.830 --> 00:19:09.290
It what?

00:19:10.590 --> 00:19:13.690
Next I activate the spell
card Monster Reborn

00:19:13.690 --> 00:19:17.390
so come on back utopia!

00:19:17.830 --> 00:19:19.760
Yeah, way to go, bronk!

00:19:19.760 --> 00:19:23.860
Wait, what is
going on here?

00:19:26.830 --> 00:19:28.660
Way to duel, bronk!

00:19:28.660 --> 00:19:29.660
Hold on,

00:19:29.660 --> 00:19:31.130
you are my servant!

00:19:31.130 --> 00:19:35.830
Yeah his body, but not his
mind. You said it yourself!

00:19:35.830 --> 00:19:37.460
See, it's gearspring
catapult that's the key

00:19:37.460 --> 00:19:38.760
to winning this match.

00:19:38.760 --> 00:19:41.690
If you destroyed it, I
wouldn't have had a chance!

00:19:41.690 --> 00:19:44.690
That's why yuma pretended to
be your mindless servant.

00:19:44.690 --> 00:19:46.290
To trick you into
forgetting about my

00:19:46.290 --> 00:19:47.660
catapult!

00:19:47.660 --> 00:19:49.160
I do not believe it!

00:19:49.160 --> 00:19:53.430
You better believe it. The only
people I serve are my buddies.

00:19:53.430 --> 00:19:56.730
I now activate gearspring
catapult's effect!

00:19:56.730 --> 00:19:59.030
By Removing one
gearspring counter,

00:19:59.030 --> 00:20:03.290
utopia gains 500 attack points!

00:20:06.560 --> 00:20:09.030
I do not like this!

00:20:09.030 --> 00:20:10.830
Well then you're gonna
positively hate

00:20:10.830 --> 00:20:12.430
what's coming up next!

00:20:12.430 --> 00:20:13.590
Do Ya feel it, bronk?

00:20:13.590 --> 00:20:14.760
I sure do!

00:20:14.760 --> 00:20:18.030
You bet. I'm feeling the flow!

00:20:25.330 --> 00:20:27.030
This cannot be!

00:20:27.030 --> 00:20:30.230
Go Rising sun slash!

00:20:37.560 --> 00:20:39.760
No way...I... I lost?

00:20:39.760 --> 00:20:41.060
Impossible!

00:20:41.060 --> 00:20:43.030
Hey Yuma, heads up!

00:20:43.030 --> 00:20:47.130
Thanks!

00:20:48.430 --> 00:20:51.560
Whoa...

00:21:02.960 --> 00:21:04.630
you did it, bronk!

00:21:04.630 --> 00:21:07.990
Thanks, pal!

00:21:08.960 --> 00:21:12.190
And Thanks for setting me up for
that way awesome Combo move!

00:21:12.190 --> 00:21:15.790
Uh...Yeah, it's
uh my pleasure.

00:21:15.790 --> 00:21:18.930
Oh, it was astral's idea, huh?

00:21:18.930 --> 00:21:20.890
No way, of course not!

00:21:20.890 --> 00:21:24.230
Astral Had nothing to do with
it, ya know, for the most part.

00:21:24.230 --> 00:21:25.560
I knew it.

00:21:25.560 --> 00:21:27.890
I figured it was too
smart a plan for you!

00:21:27.890 --> 00:21:30.390
What?
How dare you!

00:21:30.390 --> 00:21:32.630
I bet you wish you
were half as smart as me!

00:21:32.630 --> 00:21:34.830
Well yuma, I'm smart
enough to take that bet.

00:21:34.830 --> 00:21:36.390
Why I oughta...

00:21:36.390 --> 00:21:37.860
only friends so close
