00:21:37.860 --> 00:21:39.060
Take it back!

00:21:39.060 --> 00:21:40.290
You gotta lotta nerve!

00:21:40.290 --> 00:21:41.690
I demand an apology!

00:21:41.690 --> 00:21:44.433
If only all fighting could
